		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You're correct about that. It's just a shame that many clones are poorly constructed with the mentioned problems. 
<br />
<br />About the TG16/PCE, it's a shame no one has yet cloned it. Probably due to its lesser popularity and also because it would be wise to clone the CDROM too given the number of great games that are CD or Super CD. If one were to dream though, cloning the DUO but with the Super Grafx hardware and Arcade Card built in would be the coolest.

		

